{
  "stem": "10272.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Odd jobs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Odd jobs, because I got also this fight at the-- boy at the company with this-- he was always, always drunk and cursing in Jewish Jews, and-- and teasing me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wants to start up a fight with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told my boss, I cannot work in this-- this way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He starts to-- he wants to fight with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I cannot come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, he says, he cannot do anything with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He needs him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you will- maybe later, you will come, and he will get over the whole-- the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, I was doing odd jobs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this, I was doing for a few months till 1944, when in March the German Army invaded Hungary-- Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- I remember it was snowing at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the tanks came, moved into Budapest on the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were not welcomed very enthusiastically as they used to be, as I was-- as I noticed before in other places.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very calm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were watching from the windows, these tanks, German tanks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And next day on the street were posters, huge posters, about all kind of orders from the Gestapo, and from the city hall, and from the-- from the government, from the-- from the King about--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Orders about the new rules.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are now not invaded, he says.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are now joining the fight against-- against our common enemy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The President says that, Horthy, and the government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We should cooperate with the-- with the German authorities and not to do trouble.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we should also, they should tell somebody who is committing some trouble, who was a troublemaker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So- in the same-- and on the same level also, Jewish were named Jewish councils were named, to take care of-- of the-- of the-- who should be in touch, who should communicate with the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because not every Jew can go and-- and talk to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It has to be a Jewish council who represent the Jewish community of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in this-- in this Jewish council, they call it-- the German called it Judenrat, in German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is a Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the members of this council were these two professors, who-- who I was under their-- who know me from before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a Mr.-- the professor Pastor and Nemes and others like Stern was-- was some-- Rabbi Stern and all kind of rabbis who were chief-- who-- who conducted all kind of negotiations with Eichmann, who came to Hungary to talk about this Jewish problem, as they call it, resettlement of the Jews and do everything.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- so these rabbis, this-- this Jewish councils, the Judenrat, also put up posters asking the Jewish-- the Jewish residents of Budapest to conduct themselves in an orderly way, not to do trouble, and-- and everything should be-- should remain under control.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Otherwise, the Germans will see that we are-- we are not a good community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we'll have troubles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- and the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what happened to me next is that I-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a poster about-- about putting up Jewish yellow-- Jewish stars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every Jew from this and this age should-- [INAUDIBLE] what size this yellow star should be and on what part of the body, of the jacket should be.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything has to be like it was according to the order.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, I was [INAUDIBLE] I took this-- I put up this yellow star on my jacket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- other star-- other poster saying the Jews who-- who don't want to be bother-- don't want to be under some kind of a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] stress or some kind of a danger from-- from-- from somebody else, should move in the Jewish area, that we are protected.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call it a protected-- they didn't say ghetto, protected area for Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People who wants to be under the protection of the Jewish council should move in in this area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I moved to this area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the Kazinczy area they called it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a Jewish synagogue who was also vandalized when I came there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got a place to live in this backyard, on the back yard of the-- of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a guard at the-- at the gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't get out when I wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was there trapped in this thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I saw another sign, another poster, after a few weeks I was in this ghetto, that this and this youngster who was born 1922 and 1923 should report to this and this place for serving in the labor-- for labor.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
